    dc:description "Fig. 5 (opposite page). Mesopolobus robiniae Lakatos & László sp. nov. a–b, e–f, i. ♀ (MZBBU HYM000034). c–d, g–h, j. ♂ (MZBBU HYM000035). k. Paratype, ♀ (MZBBU HYM000014). l. ♂ (MZBBU HYM000036). a. Head, frontal view. b. Antenna. c. Head, frontal view. d. Antenna. e. Mesosoma. f. Fore wing. g. Mesosoma. h. Fore wing. i. Gaster, dorsal view. j. Gaster, dorsal view. k. Habitus. l. Habitus. Scale bars: a–j = 0.1 mm; l–k = 0.5 mm" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4644007/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

